PrecisOrder postponing the date upon which the COMMISSION OF INQUIRY into the BLOOD SYSTEM IN CANADA shall submit its final report to the Governor in Council from April 30, 1997 to no later than eight weeks after the Supreme Court of Canada has rendered its decision in respect of an appeal of a decision of the Federal Court of Canada concerning the Commission.
